pageContext.claim: “I think a lot of the leaks are not leaks; they're made up by the newspapers.”
pageContext.analysis: Reputable news organizations do not make up sources or leaks, and Trump has no evidence that they do. Furthermore, dozens of leaks about his administration have turned out to be accurate. Trump himself has a history of being an anonymous source for stories and has made a mission out of uprooting leakers in his White House.
